PALM LATITUDES: THE BIZ 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Sam Hall Kaplan 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Some reasons your phone calls haven't been returned yet: 
</P>
<P>
 1. They haven't read your screenplay. 
</P>
<P>
 2. They have read your screenplay. 
</P>
<P>
 3. Their secretary threw away last month's call list. 
</P>
<P>
 4. Your secretary's name is Heidi. 
</P>
<P>
 5. Your name is Heidi. 
</P>
<P>
 6. They haven't heard yet that you've just signed a three-picture deal with a 
studio. 
</P>
<P>
 7. They heard that your father wants to direct your next picture. 
</P>
<P>
 8. You spelled the producer's name wrong on 2,000 release prints. 
</P>
<P>
 9. They saw you on Howard Stern's New Year's Eve show. 
</P>
<P>
 10. They're not interested in remaking "Billy Jack" as a dramatic vehicle for 
Whoopi. Sam Hall Kaplan 
</P>
