<DOCNO> LA031394-0094 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 022261 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 13, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Westside; Part J; Page 3; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
