<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 13, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 20; Column 3 
</P>
</SECTION>
