<DOCNO> LA031394-0224 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 022391 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 13, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
