for Huntington Beach (4-1). Cypress is 3-2. 
</P>
<P>
 In consolation games: 
</P>
<P>
 La Quinta 8, Los Alamitos 7 (13 innings) -- La Quinta (3-2) scored three runs 
in the bottom of the 12th with two outs to tie the score, 7-7, then won in the 
13th. 
</P>
<P>
 Anaheim 8, Riverside North 7 -- Anaheim (2-3) scored three runs in the bottom 
of the seventh with two outs. 
</P>
<P>
