<TEXT>
<P>
 Councilman Mark Ridley-Thomas will be the host of an Empowerment Congress 
meeting from 8:30 a.m. to 1 p.m. Saturday, at Crenshaw High School. 
</P>
<P>
 The meeting is part of the 8th District councilman's ongoing "Campaign for a 
