POOL TOURNAMENT TO AID QUAKE VICTIMS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A pool tournament featuring more than 30 celebrities playing amateur players 
will take place March 19 to benefit South-Central victims of the Jan. 17 
earthquake. 
</P>
