Drexel: North Atlantic Hawaii: WAC James Madison: Colonial Liberty: Big South 
Loyola Maryland: Metro Atlantic Massachusetts: Atlantic 10 Navy: Patriot Ohio: 
Mid-American Pennsylvania: Ivy Pepperdine: West Coast Rider: Northeast Southern 
